## JSON Instance Essentials

**Instance structure:**
```json
{
  "data": {
    "type": "card",
    "attributes": {
      "title": "My Title",
      "price": 29.99
    },
    "relationships": {
      "author": {
        "links": { "self": "../Author/jane-doe" }
      }
    },
    "meta": {
      "adoptsFrom": {
        "module": "../blog-post",
        "name": "BlogPost"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

**linksToMany pattern:**
```json
"teamMembers.0": { "links": { "self": "../Person/kai" } },
"teamMembers.1": { "links": { "self": "../Person/esperanza" } }
```

**Empty linksToMany:**
```json
"items": { "links": { "self": null } }
```

**Paths:** Relative, no extensions
- Module: `"../author"` not `"../author.gts"`
- Instance: `"../Author/jane"` not `"../Author/jane.json"`

