# JSON Instance Format

## Root Structure

All data wrapped in a `data` object with:
* `type`: Always `"card"` for instances
* `attributes`: Field values
* `relationships`: Links to other cards
* `meta.adoptsFrom`: Connection to GTS definition

## Instance Template

```json
{
  "data": {
    "type": "card",
    "attributes": {
      "title": "My Title",
      "price": 29.99
    },
    "relationships": {
      "author": {
        "links": {
          "self": "../Author/jane-doe"
        }
      }
    },
    "meta": {
      "adoptsFrom": {
        "module": "../blog-post",
        "name": "BlogPost"
      }
    }
  }
}
```

## Relationship Patterns

**Single link (linksTo):**
```json
"author": {
  "links": { "self": "../Author/dr-nakamura" }
}
```

**Multiple links (linksToMany):**
```json
"teamMembers.0": {
  "links": { "self": "../Person/kai" }
},
"teamMembers.1": {
  "links": { "self": "../Person/esperanza" }
}
```

**Empty linksToMany:**
```json
"nextLevels": {
  "links": { "self": null }
}
```

## File Organization

### Single App
```
my-realm/
├── blog-post.gts
├── author.gts
├── BlogPost/
│   └── hello-world.json
└── Author/
    └── jane-doe.json
```

### Related Cards App
```
my-realm/
├── ecommerce/
│   ├── product.gts
│   ├── order.gts
│   ├── Product/
│   │   └── laptop-pro.json
│   └── Order/
│       └── order-001.json
└── shared/
    └── address-field.gts
```

## Path Conventions

* **Module paths:** Relative, no `.gts` extension
  * `"../author"` or `"../../shared/address-field"`
* **Relationship paths:** Relative, no `.json` extension
  * `"../Author/jane-doe"`
* **Date formats:**
  * DateField: `"2024-11-15"`
  * DatetimeField: `"2024-11-15T10:00:00Z"`
